    <div class="section-contents">
        <ul>
            <li>
                1) Complete and save the Departmental Admin Request form. (The previous page.)
            </li>
            <li>
                2) Watch the videos in the links below.
            </li>
            <li>
                3) Decide on the Organizational structure and where you will want to create administrative workgroups. We have provided an online tool to help with this, but you may find it easier to just draw it on paper.
            </li>
            <li>
                4) When you are ready to test out your skills, <strong>submit a help ticket</strong> <a class="button" href="https://caeshelp.ucdavis.edu/?appname=OPP&Subject=PrePurchasing - Ready for Training">Help Ticket</a> with a subject line like "PrePurchasing - Ready for Training". We will email you when we have created an account for you on the training system. You will then have about a week to create some workgroups, and some orders for those workgroups. <strong>Note!</strong> The information on this training version is cleared out every week or so. The workgroups you set up here do not have to be 100% complete, they are intended for you to test out features. Only the production version of PrePurchasing will send out emails, so you don't have to worry about making mistakes.
            </li>          
        </ul>
    
     
